# Security Policy

{{> header}}

## Reporting a Vulnerability

If you discover a security vulnerability in **{{projectName}}**, please report it
privately by emailing the project maintainers. **Do not** disclose it publicly
until a fix has been released.

Please include the following details in your report:

- A description of the vulnerability
- Steps to reproduce
- Affected versions
- Any potential impact

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported          |
|---------|--------------------|
| Latest  | :white_check_mark: |
| Older   | :x:                |

## Disclosure Timeline

We aim to respond within 48 hours and release a fix within 7 days of confirmation.

